commitResults.messageTitle: Implement task persistence using file storage
commitResults.messageBody: The task list is now persisted to disk using a file (./data/Nova.txt). This allows tasks to be saved between sessions, so the user's task list is preserved when the program is closed and reopened.  Handles file creation and directory creation if they don't exist.
